      "amount": "2 stalks, sliced"
    },
    {
      "name": "ground black pepper",
      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180 degrees celsius.",
    "Press tofu to remove excess moisture and cut into cubes.",
    "In a bowl mix tofu cubes with soy sauce, biryani masala, sesame oil, minced garlic, pepper.",
    "Spread tofu evenly on a baking sheet lined with parchment.",
    "Bake tofu for 20 minutes, turning halfway.",
    "While tofu bakes, reheat cooked rice and stir in a pinch of biryani masala.",
    "When tofu is golden, remove from oven and toss with cooked rice and green onions.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with extra green onions if desired."
